    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major restoration project or a source for spare parts. The engine is currently non-operational and will require an extensive overhaul, and the transmission shows signs of severe wear. Externally, the body has significant rust patches, several large dents, and the paint has faded considerably. The interior requires a complete deep clean and upholstery repair due to multiple tears and heavy staining. Buyers should expect to tow this vehicle from the lot.",
